STATE of North Carolina
v.
Cornelius TUCKER, Jr. No. 118P01-10. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 22, 2004. Cornelius Tucker, Jr., for Tucker. Christopher W. Brooks, Assistant Attorney General, Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 21st day of July 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Forsyth County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd day of July 2004."
